<section id="about" class="section--white text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center mb-6">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h5 class="section--title">Who is this Gordon Guy?</h5>
        <p>That question is usually best answered with what I'm working on at the time the quesiton is asked. Currently, I'm situated with an exciting, young startup we've dubbed <a href="https://wirkn.com" target="_blank">Wirkn</a>. There I head up the product and engineering team as the company's CPO.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row justify-content-center mb-6">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h5 class="section--title">Getting Here...</h5>
        <p>Ten years ago, I stepped foot on <a href="https://uwaterloo.ca" target="_blank">UWaterloo</a> campus for the first time. With a graphing calculator in one hand and a Big Gulp in the other. I couldn't have been more excited about my future in Mechanical Engineering.<p>
          <p>Little did I know that just one year later I'd be trading my iron ring in for late nights with my trusty MacBook on a beat-up couch, in a colorfully decorated startup office.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center mb-6">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h5 class="section--title">And Now...?</h5>
          <p>Since then I've helped grow, sell and gracefully bring to a close and a number of startup companies across North Ameria.</p>
          <p>I invite you to enjoy reading some of my stories and to checkout my hobby projects.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

